Description: A set of tools to train and evaluate the SCARF model into a given
    dataset, avoiding the need to rely on Python.
    Objetive. trained_model <- train(dataset)
    Objective. results <- downstream(trained_model, dataset)
    Objective. latent_features <- get_features(trained_model, dataset)
